{"tid":1073201,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"一人一首國語版好聽過粵語版嘅歌","createTime":"2019-03-22T13:42:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T10:54:26.000Z","uid":63821,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"38c35751263cc1405fdcbb5f35ee64bb6e6e1d51","tid":1073201,"uid":63821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:42:01.000Z","msg":"好多香港歌手出歌會有兩份詞，一首廣東話一首國語。但聽嚟聽去都係覺得廣東話好聽啲。<br />\n<br />\n陳奕迅&lt;明年今日&gt;完勝&lt;十年&gt;呢啲就唔使講啦，但連林宥嘉呢個台灣人出廣東歌&lt;壞與更壞&gt;我都係覺得正過國語嘅&lt;勿忘你&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底有冇一首歌係國語正過廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係同一個歌手嘅歌（e.g.牙醫面具VS陳勢安天后）因為會受歌手唱功影響就唔計住~"},{"pid":"2cccfa6dee4c4e516b6efb42dc852af8b89ea767","tid":1073201,"uid":22141,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"紅豆"},{"pid":"3a69118ce641df3bcd5b17393b3999ca97573c19","tid":1073201,"uid":68592,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"張國榮首 我"},{"pid":"7e8599b66287afcfc101a9baa557bc264b6721ef","tid":1073201,"uid":62717,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"愛情轉移 我覺得更有feel，可能淺白啲"},{"pid":"213259b00c2af9565a14fb4377ad918115f286cc","tid":1073201,"uid":20246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"齊秦 大約在冬季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce8d89903ac79c63e926a49f05c07dbbbb75713","tid":1073201,"uid":142383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"聖誕結"},{"pid":"d0e93e1e9f2a98dbe9c62e402c318534c7850cf1","tid":1073201,"uid":238697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-